Google Ads API Tool - Design Document

Company: Purety Family Naturopathic Corporation
Website: https://puretyclinic.com
MCC ID: 895-729-9346

1. Overview
We are building an internal campaign monitoring and optimization tool for our naturopathic medical clinic. The tool will allow our team to view campaign performance metrics, analyze ad effectiveness, and make data-driven decisions to improve our advertising ROI.

2. Features
- Read campaign performance data (impressions, clicks, cost, conversions)
- Generate performance reports for internal review
- Monitor ad group and keyword performance
- Track conversion metrics from our website contact forms

3. API Usage
We will use the following Google Ads API resources:
- GoogleAdsService.Search - to query campaign, ad group, and ad performance data
- CustomerService - to retrieve account information
- CampaignService - to read campaign settings and status

4. Data Flow
Website (puretyclinic.com) -> Contact Form Submissions -> Conversion Tracking
Google Ads API -> Campaign Data -> Internal Dashboard -> Staff Review

5. Users
Internal staff only (clinic administrators and marketing team).
No external users will have access to the tool.

6. Rate Limiting
We anticipate low API usage (under 1000 operations per day) for periodic
reporting and monitoring purposes only.

7. Data Storage
Campaign performance data may be cached locally for reporting purposes.
No customer PII is collected or stored through the API.
All API credentials are stored securely using environment variable encryption.
